{
  "stem": "6845.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only way we shall go to the gymnasium, if we can live together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she knew that I have to go and stay someplace, because my parents still  lived in Sobrance.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was arranged.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went, and I don't know how much they paid for my room and board.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And oh, it was just real honeymoon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just fun, fun, crazy fun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And well, luckily, the lady was a good-natured lady and liked me, and I liked her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were two devils, and I didn't-- I can't believe it, how they could stand us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, she would crawl on the top-- the toilet was outdoors in Europe-- not in [NON-ENGLISH], actually.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm surprised, now that I'm saying it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When we moved into the cit-- even in [INAUDIBLE], even in the small village of Sobrance-- I'm sorry-- our toilet was part of the house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it seems that wasn't the standard, because when I moved into Uzhorod and stayed with this family, the-- I cannot call it bathroom.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was just strictly a-- um, uh, I wish I could think on it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was th-- it was no bathtub, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just an outhouse, but I never saw it before, so I was kind of fascinated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's outside, you know, and it's-- so what happened, one day we came home from school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we did some drawings and everything, and Martha says, I like yours, and you like mine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why don't we hang them up, and-- so we can enjoy and look at it?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we decided, took it to the outhouse in her house, put it on the-- I shouldn't speak about such subjects.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not so delightful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, she jumped on the top, and she almost fell all the way down.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
